text: Elisabeth "Liesje" Schreinemacher (born 13 May 1983) is a Dutch lawyer and politician. She is a member of the People's Party for Freedom and Democracy (VVD). She was Minister for Foreign Trade and Development Cooperation from 10 January 2022 to 2 July 2024. She was a Member of the European Parliament from 2019 until 2022. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Ministers of foreign affairs of the Netherlands Category:MEPs for the Netherlands Category:Politicians from Rotterdam Category:Dutch lawyers Category:People's Party for Freedom and Democracy politicians
